      <title>工会谈判进入第四轮 大众汽车遭遇更多罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/vw-faces-more-costly-walkouts-as-union-talks-enter-fourth-round</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车公司工人于周一举行罢工，工会领导人威胁说，如果与管理层的谈判未能取得突破，他们将升级抗议活动，以抗议该汽车制造商同名品牌的痛苦裁员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/vw-faces-more-costly-walkouts-as-union-talks-enter-fourth-round</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
